Truly, as I said in the MC earlier...

941
01:25:51,194 --> 01:25:55,194
AZKiちゃん、本当にシンガーとして尊敬してて...
I really respect AZKi-chan as a singer...

942
01:25:55,194 --> 01:25:58,694
